text.section:
Each association that holds a certificate of filing from the commissioner shall be subject to the following:
All assessments placed on insurers under KRS 304.17B-021;
All rating restrictions placed on employer-organized associations under KRS 304.17A-0954;
All rate review requirements placed on insurers under this subtitle;
All data collection requirements placed on insurers under this subtitle; and
Provisions of Subtitle 12 of this chapter that apply to health insurers.
